Reasoning: 
1. cs.CV (Computer Vision): The paper proposes a method for learning joint embeddings of images and text, which is a common topic in computer vision research. 
2. cs.CL (Computation and Language): The paper deals with text-to-image and image-to-text retrieval, which is a natural language processing task. 
3. cs.MM (Multimedia): The paper deals with multimedia data (images and text) and proposes a method for learning joint embeddings. 
4. cs.IR (Information Retrieval): The paper deals with retrieval tasks (image-to-text and text-to-image) and proposes a method for learning embeddings that can improve retrieval accuracy. 
5. cs.LG (Machine Learning): The paper proposes a neural network-based method for learning joint embeddings, which falls under the category of machine learning.
